s the sole possession/use of that object; the other party forfeits the use/possession of that same object and holds no security guaranteeing its return.In the case of a govt. bond sale both parties have access, possession and continuous use of the same object (asset), albeit in different forms.\nI too fail to see how bond transaction has any significant impact on inflation - the associated interest payment perhaps adds marginally to both or either supply/demand (more likely adds to speculative investment), while the 'sequestered' funds add to the supply base of an active secondary market.", "recommendation_count": "1", "in_reply_to": "123247944", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "123256775", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1543827384000}, "author": "ElCanGuru", "author_id": "100090226", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Unfortunately, Scomo has done the opposite. He in fact intervened to ensure Kelly remains as the sitting member to the next election. Showing his true colours. Plea to the voters of Hughes: please, please get rid of Craig Kelly in a few months time.", "recommendation_count": "6", "in_reply_to": "123255988", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "123256384", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1543826168000}, "author": "ElCanGuru", "author_id": "100090226", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Whatever happened to Jobson Grothe and his younger sibling Ina Vayshon? At least they were good for a laugh. All we are left with these days, is a Morrison/Abbott/Kelly version of their new catchphrase: \"Back to the fifties!\"", "recommendation_count": "5", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "123246077", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1543786328000}, "author": "harjiboy", "author_id": "4111938", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "They also want the anti corruption bill passed.", "recommendation_count": "0", "in_reply_to": "123225593", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "123246070", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1543786316000}, "author